{"article_id":"u7WSvRh1RYYrv61x","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ' s former campaign chairman Paul Manafort was sent to jail Friday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"after a federal judge revoked his $ 10 million bail in the wake of witness-tampering charges","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"lodged by special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Washington , DC , District Court Judge Amy Berman Jackson granted a motion","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"filed by federal prosecutors","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and ordered","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that the accused felon be locked up until his trial on money-laundering and other charges in September .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"see also","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Manafort hit with new charges in Russia probe","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Paul Manafort was hit with a second superseding indictment Friday ...","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"\" You have abused the trust","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"placed in you six months ago , \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the judge told Manafort ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"referring to his earlier deal for house arrest .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"She scolded the former Trump aide over the feds ' allegations","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that he used his cellphone","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to try to contact case witnesses","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"and persuade them to lie .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"\" This is not middle school .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"I can ' t take away his cellphone , \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"\" If I tell him not to call 56 witnesses ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"will he call the 57th ? \"","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"And she refuted charges","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"leveled by the commander-in-chief","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that Manafort ' s prosecution was motivated by politics .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"\" This hearing is not about politics .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"It is not about the conduct of the office of special counsel .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"It is about the defendant ' s conduct , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Jackson said .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"\" I ' m concerned","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"you seem to treat these proceedings as another marketing exercise . \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Prosecutor Greg Andres told the judge","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that Manafort , 69 , could continue to commit crimes","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"if he remained free on bail ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"calling his actions \" a sustained campaign over a five-week period \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to reach two witnesses","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"in an attempt","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to persuade them to lie on his behalf .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Three US marshals led Manafort out of the courtroom and into the prisoners ' holding area after the judge ' s ruling .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"A marshal then returned","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"to give Manafort ' s wife her spouse ' s wallet , belt and necktie , typical procedures","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"to prevent detainees from committing suicide ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The Washington Post reported .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Trump took to Twitter","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"to condemn what he called Manafort ' s \" sentence ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" though his former adviser has not been tried yet , never mind convicted and sentenced .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"\" Wow , what a tough sentence for Paul Manafort ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"who has represented Ronald Reagan , Bob Dole and many other top political people and campaigns .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Didn ' t know","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Manafort was the head of the Mob .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"What about Comey and Crooked Hillary and all of the others ?","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Very unfair ! \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Trump said earlier Friday","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"that he felt badly for his former campaign chair","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and minimized his role in the campaign .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" Paul Manafort worked for me for a very short period of time .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"He worked for Ronald Reagan .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"He worked for Bob Dole .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"He worked for John McCain ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"or his firm did .","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"He worked for many other Republicans .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"He worked for me , what , for 49 days or something ?","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"A very short period of time , \"","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"\" I feel badly about a lot of it","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"because I think","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"a lot of it is very unfair .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"They went back 12 years","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"to get things","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that he did 12 years ago , \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Prosecutors argued","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that Manafort","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"- who has done extensive work in Ukraine and elsewhere in Europe -","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"was a significant flight risk .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"His attorney , Richard Westling , had urged no jail ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"but Jackson was unswayed by his arguments .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Political allies argue","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that Mueller is sticking it to Manafort","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"to pressure him into cooperating in the probe of Russian election meddling and collusion by the Trump campaign .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Last week , Mueller ' s team of investigators charged","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"that Manafort had tried to persuade two witnesses in the case to lie about their lobbying efforts on his behalf in the US .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Manafort also pleaded not guilty to the two charges","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"levied against him last week for witness tampering and conspiracy","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"to obstruct justice .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Prosecutors say","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Manafort was engaged in a broad conspiracy","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"to launder more than $ 30 million","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"he was paid","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"for secretly lobbying for a pro-Russian former politician and party in Ukraine .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"He faces additional charges in Virginia of tax evasion , bank fraud and failure to report foreign bank accounts .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Trump refused to say Friday","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"if he might pardon Manafort","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"if he ' s convicted .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"\" I don ' t want to talk about that , \"","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"the president told reporters at the White House .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Related Video","depth":2},{"id":99,"text":"Video length 31 seconds :31","depth":3},{"id":100,"text":"Paul Manafort walks into court","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"as people yell","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"\" lock him up ! \"","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Paul Manafort walks into court","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"as people yell","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"\" lock him up ! \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":203,"right":210,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":149,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":114,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":112,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":108,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":0,"right":107,"relation":"context","nuc